with(XmlSuite) - Method in class dev.aherscu.qa.jgiven.reporter.AbstractQaJgivenReporter
Builds a new reporter configured per following TestNG XML suite parameters: referenceTag the reference tag identifier, or AbstractQaJgivenReporter.DEFAULT_REFERENCE_TAG screenshotScale the screenshot scale to apply when embedding files into reports, or AbstractQaJgivenReporter.DEFAULT_SCREENSHOT_SCALE datePattern the date pattern to use for presenting dates, or AbstractQaJgivenReporter.DEFAULT_DATE_PATTERN templateResourceXXX the template resource file name to apply; the XXX is the concrete reporter implementation name (class)
